---
title: Korean BBQ Veggie Mince with Green Beans, Jasmine Rice and Crispy Onions
description: This Korean BBQ Veggie Mince is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R11_W32_UK_F17213-5_MME_Main_low-4455ff64.jpg
